title: Phase II Lighting Improvements Around UC’s Uptown Campus Underway (University of Cincinnati)
text: ( Source : University of Cincinnati ) Phase II Lighting Improvements Around UC's Uptown Campus Underway Lighting enhancements part of plan to improve campus and community safety. Phase II includes lighting on 30 streets. Photos By: Jay Yocis,
